messages.message: is there any content anywhere on how to build applications for Instabase? (for instance: I'd like to build a small application on Instabase that would allow my sales engineers to experiment visually with some computer vision techniques (like thresholding, gray-scaling, noise reduction, etc.)). do we have any such "*getting started with building applications on Instabase*" anywhere?
So a Custom UI? Does the readme in this repo help: https://github.com/instabase/custom-ui-template
Yes! that looks like a great start. thank you so much @Jessica!
